<i>Wow. This is really-
I don't- I can't-</i>

19:00.828 --> 19:02.996
<i>Oh, no, no, no. It's good, it's good.</i>

19:03.131 --> 19:04.231
<i>It's great.</i>

19:04.365 --> 19:05.364
<i>You're fine.</i>

19:05.499 --> 19:06.465
<i>Hi, I'm Gus.</i>

19:06.600 --> 19:07.666
<i>Yeah, I know.</i>

19:07.801 --> 19:09.101
<i>Thank you.</i>

19:10.670 --> 19:11.770
<i>Bye.</i>

19:11.904 --> 19:13.638
<i>Thank you.
Nice meeting you.</i>

19:30.087 --> 19:32.220
<i>Nice job, Rodney.</i>

20:39.445 --> 20:40.612
<i>Alfred
I promise...</i>

20:40.746 --> 20:42.847
<i>I'll eat
something else tomorrow.</i>

21:32.290 --> 21:34.891
<i>Abe, are you out there?</i>

21:35.025 --> 21:38.361
<i>Abe! Are you all right?</i>

21:38.495 --> 21:40.528
<i>Hey, have you seen
a lone fisherman?</i>

21:40.663 --> 21:43.531
<i>Sorry. I haven't
seen anyone.</i>

21:43.666 --> 21:45.934
<i>Abe!</i>

21:46.068 --> 21:50.671
<i>Abe!</i>

21:50.805 --> 21:54.474
<i>Abe, where are you?</i>

21:54.608 --> 21:57.510
<i>Abe, come on!</i>

22:00.446 --> 22:02.414
<i>Abe!</i>

22:58.629 --> 22:59.796
<i>Oh!</i>

23:12.341 --> 23:14.208
<i>Oh!</i>

24:24.835 --> 24:28.405
<i>There's one thing
you can say about nature.</i>

24:28.539 --> 24:32.975
<i>If you make one lousy rule
to describe it...</i>

24:33.109 --> 24:37.078
<i>it'll contradict you even if
it has to bust its ass to do so.</i>

24:37.212 --> 24:41.949
<i>And so what? If anybody ever
discovered the real laws of nature...</i>

24:42.084 --> 24:44.284
<i>nature would rear back
and strike him dead...</i>

24:44.419 --> 24:45.952
<i>before he could
pass on the news.</i>

24:46.087 --> 24:47.821
<i>Jesus Christ.</i>

24:47.955 --> 24:50.523
<i>No. I think
his name is Abe.</i>

24:52.392 --> 24:55.361
<i>Maybe Abe knew.</i>

24:55.494 --> 24:58.029
<i>Maybe he had just figured
the whole world out...</i>

24:58.164 --> 25:01.499
<i>and was about to tell me
as I floated past.</i>

25:01.634 --> 25:04.568
<i>But God caught wind of it and
stuck out His invisible foot...</i>

25:04.702 --> 25:07.204
<i>tripped and drowned him.</i>

25:09.373 --> 25:12.442
<i>If the fool only knew
how to swim.</i>

25:24.453 --> 25:27.954
<i>Easy, friend.</i>

25:28.089 --> 25:31.391
<i>Let's see if we can
thaw you out.</i>

25:38.798 --> 25:40.132
<i>I am Titus.</i>

25:40.266 --> 25:44.068
<i>Titus I rving Gerrard.
At your service.</i>

25:44.203 --> 25:47.504
<i>Nice to meet you. I...</i>

25:47.638 --> 25:48.839
<i>am simply Gus.</i>

25:48.973 --> 25:50.774
<i>Simply Gus?
I don't think so.</i>

25:50.908 --> 25:52.342
<i>Anyone who knows
the secrets...</i>

25:52.477 --> 25:54.076
<i>to the catches
you made today...</i>

25:54.211 --> 25:55.311
<i>is not simply anything.</i>

25:55.445 --> 25:57.146
<i>There's no secrets
to those catches.</i>

25:57.280 --> 25:59.415
<i>The trout I caught
on a wet fly.</i>

25:59.549 --> 26:01.783
<i>The corpse I caught
on a soggy dry.</i>

26:01.917 --> 26:03.151
<i>Yes, well...</i>

26:03.285 --> 26:06.454
<i>you've done old Abe's
family some service...</i>

26:06.589 --> 26:07.921
<i>by collecting his remains.</i>

26:08.056 --> 26:10.858
<i>And since we're all bodily
destined for corpsehood...</i>

26:10.992 --> 26:13.227
<i>and spiritually possessed
of immortal souls...</i>

26:13.361 --> 26:16.496
<i>I see no reason to let the
proximity of corpses ruin our day.</i>

26:16.630 --> 26:19.132
<i>If you think we're all
possessed by immortal souls...</i>

26:19.266 --> 26:20.665
<i>I'd sure like
to see them.</i>

26:20.800 --> 26:23.869
<i>Maybe you're looking
in the wrong places.</i>

26:35.579 --> 26:38.515
<i>For clear vision.</i>

26:38.649 --> 26:40.182
<i>Thanks.</i>

26:40.316 --> 26:42.651
<i>M m-hm.</i>

26:42.785 --> 26:46.387
<i>And uh,
thanks for the ride.</i>

27:25.621 --> 27:27.422
<i>A fisherman is dead.</i>

27:30.560 --> 27:34.061
<i>Everyone I know
will one day be dead.</i>

27:34.196 --> 27:35.996
<i>What can I do about it?</i>

27:36.131 --> 27:39.032
<i>Death is the most natural
thing there is...</i>

27:39.166 --> 27:41.768
<i>and we all have a knack for
it. The only question is...</i>

27:41.902 --> 27:45.671
<i>when we'll master it.
Doesn't matter what we do...</i>

27:45.805 --> 27:48.273
<i>or what we don't do.</i>

27:51.376 --> 27:55.713
<i>This is no passing thought.</i>

27:55.847 --> 28:00.217
<i>It's a gnawing emptiness
more real than the cold.</i>

28:18.566 --> 28:21.868
<i>This is bullshit.</i>

28:23.870 --> 28:26.105
<i>Ma tossed
the baby rabbit skeleton...</i>

28:26.240 --> 28:27.907
<i>I had hanging in my closet.</i>

28:35.615 --> 28:37.548
<i>Is that tonight's dreefee?</i>

28:37.682 --> 28:38.949
<i>Yep.</i>

28:39.084 --> 28:40.851
<i>I had to get a new one.</i>

28:40.986 --> 28:44.320
<i>Whatever helps you sleep,
Bill Bob.</i>

28:44.455 --> 28:45.488
<i>Gussy?</i>

28:45.623 --> 28:48.324
<i>Bill Bob?</i>

28:48.459 --> 28:50.058
<i>I thought it might make
you feel better...</i>

28:50.193 --> 28:52.194
<i>to explain that you've
got a garden angel.</i>

28:52.328 --> 28:53.629
<i>You mean guardian angel?</i>

28:53.763 --> 28:56.831
<i>Nah. See, you think
you're alone.</i>

28:56.965 --> 28:59.834
<i>But you're not.
You've got a garden angel...</i>

28:59.968 --> 29:02.270
<i>that's your twin.</i>

29:02.403 --> 29:04.104
<i>It's called a guardian angel.</i>

29:04.238 --> 29:06.606
<i>No. I'm talking
about a garden angel.</i>

29:06.741 --> 29:09.842
<i>It's like your shadow.</i>

29:26.724 --> 29:28.557
<i>Dreefee.</i>

29:42.904 --> 29:45.606
<i>Garden angel.</i>

29:45.740 --> 29:49.242
<i>Gussy, garden angels
come from the ground...</i>

29:49.376 --> 29:50.910
<i>like carrots.</i>

29:51.045 --> 29:52.945
<i>When they first
come out of the ground...</i>

29:53.080 --> 29:55.113
<i>into the garden world,
they're very old...</i>

29:55.248 --> 29:56.848
<i>or hurt, or sick.</i>

29:56.983 --> 29:58.550
<i>And the longer
the angels live there...</i>

29:58.685 --> 29:59.918
<i>the younger and smaller
they grow</i>

30:00.053 --> 30:01.485
<i>and happier and friendlier
they get.</i>

30:01.620 --> 30:03.120
<i>When they get little little...</i>

30:03.255 --> 30:06.123
<i>they disappear out of the garden
world and into our world...</i>

30:06.258 --> 30:07.724
<i>and we trade places.</i>

30:07.858 --> 30:09.125
<i>We what?</i>

30:09.260 --> 30:11.461
<i>We trade places
with our twin.</i>

30:11.595 --> 30:13.496
<i>We go there and our twin comes here.</i>

30:13.631 --> 30:16.799
<i>We journey up and up
through a long black tunnel...</i>

30:16.933 --> 30:19.535
<i>till we reach
the garden angel grounds.</i>

30:19.669 --> 30:21.536
<i>Sprout up like carrots.</i>

30:21.670 --> 30:24.038
<i>Trade back and forth.</i>

30:24.173 --> 30:28.442
<i>Does knowing this make you feel
a little less lonely, Gussy?</i>

30:28.576 --> 30:30.277
<i>Yeah, Bill Bob.</i>

30:30.411 --> 30:32.145
<i>Thanks.</i>

32:51.497 --> 32:52.697
<i>Oh, sorry.</i>

32:52.832 --> 32:56.301
<i>Uh, I'm, uh-</i>

32:56.434 --> 32:57.968
<i>Don't get scared.</i>

32:58.102 --> 33:03.206
<i>I'm just- I'm just
a marmless misher-</i>

33:03.340 --> 33:06.409
<i>I just came here
to go swimming.</i>

33:13.049 --> 33:14.349
<i>Oops.</i>

33:14.484 --> 33:16.217
<i>I gotta go.</i>

33:16.351 --> 33:18.519
<i>You know, um-</i>

33:18.653 --> 33:20.788
<i>Do not- Uh.</i>

33:20.922 --> 33:22.922
<i>Bye.</i>

33:36.702 --> 33:38.002
<i>Hey!</i>

33:38.136 --> 33:40.838
<i>You all right up there?</i>

33:40.973 --> 33:42.205
<i>Yeah.</i>

33:42.340 --> 33:45.141
<i>Well, are you hurt?</i>

33:45.276 --> 33:47.811
<i>I- No- No!</i>

33:49.846 --> 33:52.147
<i>Can you get down?</i>

33:52.282 --> 33:54.817
<i>No.</i>

33:54.950 --> 33:57.952
<i>Why not?</i>

33:58.087 --> 33:59.854
<i>Just 'cause.</i>

33:59.989 --> 34:01.189
<i>All right, mummy mouth.</i>

34:01.323 --> 34:03.290
<i>If that's all you got
for me, good luck.</i>

34:03.424 --> 34:06.226
<i>No, no, no.
Don't go.</i>

34:06.361 --> 34:07.960
<i>Why not?</i>

34:08.094 --> 34:09.762
<i>"No life, good scholar...</i>

34:09.897 --> 34:12.331
<i>"no life so happy
and so pleasant...</i>

34:12.466 --> 34:14.799
<i>"as the life
of a well-governed angler.</i>

34:14.934 --> 34:16.801
<i>"So we may say that God
never did make...</i>

34:16.936 --> 34:20.170
<i>"a more calm, quiet...</i>

34:20.306 --> 34:24.775
<i>innocent recreation
than angling. "</i>

34:24.909 --> 34:26.409
<i>I don't suppose he did.</i>

34:26.545 --> 34:29.746
<i>And now, I think it's time...</i>

34:29.880 --> 34:31.581
<i>for you to repair
to your angle rod...</i>

34:31.715 --> 34:34.382
<i>which should not be left in
the water to fish for itself.</i>

34:34.516 --> 34:36.784
<i>Oh, yeah, is that what
we've been doing, huh?</i>

34:36.920 --> 34:39.454
<i>Funny, 'cause I thought...</i>

34:39.589 --> 34:41.355
<i>I was trying to catch me
a steelhead.</i>

34:41.489 --> 34:45.393
<i>And you, what are you
doing here?</i>

34:45.527 --> 34:48.661
<i>I am a fisherman, but I
only came here to swim.</i>

34:48.795 --> 34:51.498
<i>If you're a fisherman,
where's your gear?</i>

34:51.632 --> 34:54.300
<i>My gear is at home,
on the Tamanawis.</i>

34:54.434 --> 34:58.904
<i>"But let us say grace
and fall to breakfast.</i>

34:59.039 --> 35:00.471
<i>What say you, scholar?"</i>

35:00.606 --> 35:02.307
<i>You can say grace
all you want.</i>

35:02.441 --> 35:04.275
<i>Just don't fall
to breakfast, please.</i>

35:04.410 --> 35:07.377
<i>Why not?</i>

35:07.512 --> 35:09.513
<i>Because you're gonna
break your neck...</i>

35:09.647 --> 35:12.349
<i>before I figure out
that lingo of yours.</i>

35:12.483 --> 35:16.886
<i>It's Zizak Waltley.
I mean Zisac Walters-</i>

35:17.020 --> 35:19.088
<i>Izaak Walton?</i>

35:19.222 --> 35:22.524
<i>Yes!</i>

35:22.658 --> 35:24.626
<i>And what is your name?</i>

35:24.760 --> 35:26.293
<i>Crawl me Gust.</i>

35:26.428 --> 35:28.796
<i>Wh-Wh-Wh-What's
your name?</i>

35:31.099 --> 35:35.401
<i>Eddy.</i>

35:35.536 --> 35:37.470
<i>Just Eddy.
Nice to meet you.</i>

35:37.605 --> 35:41.173
<i>Eddy, like the swirvles
in the river wattle.</i>

35:41.307 --> 35:43.609
<i>I wish.</i>

35:43.743 --> 35:45.543
<i>No.</i>

35:45.677 --> 35:47.745
<i>Eddy like my dad, Edwin.</i>

35:51.216 --> 35:52.949
<i>You got- You got-
You got a bite.</i>

35:53.084 --> 35:54.484
<i>Hm?</i>

36:23.877 --> 36:25.410
<i>Where'd you go?</i>

38:02.460 --> 38:04.294
<i>Aiee!</i>

38:04.428 --> 38:07.597
<i>Sacajawea Argeiphontes!
I am wounded.</i>

38:07.732 --> 38:08.764
<i>Titus?</i>

38:21.009 --> 38:23.810
<i>The Sufi Attar
has written...</i>

38:23.945 --> 38:27.147
<i>"One tiny fly which
entered the ear of Nimrod...</i>

38:27.281 --> 38:29.815
<i>troubled the brain
of that idiot for centuries. "</i>

38:29.950 --> 38:33.719
<i>Please, Gus.
Spare me Nimrod's fate.</i>

38:35.888 --> 38:37.155
<i>It's hopeless.</i>

38:37.289 --> 38:39.691
<i>I'll never catch one
of those beautiful trout.</i>

38:39.825 --> 38:41.792
<i>Whoops. You just used
one of the two words...</i>

38:41.926 --> 38:45.496
<i>that should be deleted from
every true fisherman's vocabulary.</i>

38:45.630 --> 38:46.430
<i>Hopeless?</i>

38:46.564 --> 38:49.065
<i>No. Always and never.</i>

38:51.468 --> 38:52.335
<i>How's it feel?</i>

38:52.469 --> 38:53.802
<i>Eerie, thanks.</i>

38:53.936 --> 38:54.936
<i>Don't mention it.</i>

38:55.071 --> 38:57.973
<i>Consider it de-mentioned.</i>

38:58.107 --> 39:01.041
<i>What's that?</i>

39:01.176 --> 39:03.177
<i>It's a long, dull story.</i>

39:03.311 --> 39:05.946
<i>If I'm not mistaken,
I've seen that look before.</i>

39:06.081 --> 39:09.816
<i>Is there a woman in this?</i>

39:11.418 --> 39:13.086
<i>Twice she slipped
away now.</i>

39:13.220 --> 39:15.654
<i>She's uncatchable.</i>

39:15.789 --> 39:18.323
<i>Uncatchable
as in never?</i>

39:18.458 --> 39:21.459
<i>She's not a fish, Titus.</i>

39:21.593 --> 39:23.961
<i>Maybe not, but it
certainly sounds to me...</i>

39:24.096 --> 39:26.063
<i>like you're telling the story
of the one that got away.</i>

39:26.198 --> 39:28.265
<i>Live the rest of my life
without ever seeing...</i>

39:28.399 --> 39:30.066
<i>the beautiful
fisher girl again?</i>

39:30.201 --> 39:33.769
<i>That's- that's a pretty
miserable prospect.</i>

39:33.904 --> 39:35.237
<i>Well-</i>

39:35.372 --> 39:37.139
<i>I guess there's nothing
left to do...</i>

39:37.274 --> 39:39.641
<i>but just drink
till I die.</i>

39:41.443 --> 39:44.646
<i>I'll admit there is no cure
for a soul in your condition...</i>

39:44.780 --> 39:48.615
<i>but there are
three consolations.</i>

39:48.750 --> 39:51.351
<i>Okay.</i>

39:51.486 --> 39:54.353
<i>One is hope.
You may find her again.</i>

39:54.488 --> 39:56.088
<i>Yeah, fat chance.</i>

39:56.223 --> 39:59.291
<i>Gus, if she's as beautiful
as you say she is-</i>

39:59.425 --> 40:01.493
<i>She's twice as beautiful
as I say she is.</i>

40:01.627 --> 40:04.563
<i>She knows your name.
She knows the river.</i>

40:04.697 --> 40:05.696
<i>She may find you.</i>

40:05.831 --> 40:07.598
<i>Yeah. We may grow wings.</i>

40:07.732 --> 40:09.733
<i>We might.</i>

40:09.868 --> 40:14.137
<i>Okay. What are these
other two consolations?</i>

40:14.271 --> 40:17.540
<i>Well, you've already put down
a healthy dose of the second.</i>

40:17.675 --> 40:19.908
<i>The third, however,
requires more aptitude.</i>

40:20.043 --> 40:22.110
<i>What kind of aptitudes?</i>

40:22.245 --> 40:23.612
<i>Philosophical aptitude.</i>

40:23.746 --> 40:26.781
<i>Titus, I know how
to philosophize...</i>

40:26.915 --> 40:29.483
<i>as well as you
know how to fly cast.</i>

40:29.618 --> 40:32.519
<i>I think you should
get plowed tonight.</i>

40:32.653 --> 40:36.890
<i>And tomorrow,
we begin philosophizing.</i>

40:37.024 --> 40:38.090
<i>I just told you...</i>

40:38.225 --> 40:39.859
<i>I don't know
how to philosophize.</i>

40:39.993 --> 40:43.562
<i>Well, and I don't know
how to fish.</i>

40:43.697 --> 40:45.496
<i>Okay. So?</i>

40:45.631 --> 40:47.799
<i>So we teach each other.</i>

40:50.502 --> 40:52.336
<i>What have I got to lose?</i>

40:52.470 --> 40:55.839
<i>Your unhappiness.</i>

40:55.974 --> 40:58.007
<i>Yeah, right.</i>

41:03.247 --> 41:04.412
<i>What is that?</i>

41:04.547 --> 41:07.249
<i>Is that an imitation
of a grasshopper?</i>

41:07.383 --> 41:11.087
<i>This is an abstract
representation...</i>

41:13.722 --> 41:18.458
<i>of a fat tourist
on a golf course.</i>

41:18.592 --> 41:21.794
<i>It's called Bermuda shorts.</i>

41:21.929 --> 41:23.996
<i>Here, fishy.</i>

41:24.130 --> 41:27.132
<i>I like it. What say we
migrate to a watering hole...</i>

41:27.267 --> 41:29.867
<i>a little closer
to civilization?</i>

41:30.002 --> 41:31.369
<i>To Portland?</i>

41:31.503 --> 41:32.937
<i>Sure.</i>

41:33.071 --> 41:35.873
<i>The way that goes ahead often
looks as if it went back.</i>

41:36.008 --> 41:38.575
<i>I just want to go ahead
and find Eddy.</i>

41:39.877 --> 41:41.211
<i>Come on.</i>

42:15.507 --> 42:17.341
<i>Titus?</i>

42:18.710 --> 42:19.710
<i>Titus!</i>

42:19.844 --> 42:22.478
<i>Yes?</i>

42:22.613 --> 42:24.113
<i>Ah.</i>

42:24.248 --> 42:25.682
<i>This your dog?</i>

42:25.816 --> 42:26.883
<i>Yes.</i>

42:27.017 --> 42:29.584
<i>Well, he's kind of
staring at me.</i>

42:29.719 --> 42:30.719
<i>So?</i>

42:30.853 --> 42:32.254
<i>Does he bite?
Can I move? Or-</i>

42:32.388 --> 42:33.555
<i>Why won't he just
go away?</i>

42:33.690 --> 42:36.457
<i>He
- He doesn't bite without cause.</i>

42:36.591 --> 42:38.225
<i>But, uh,
you should move.</i>

42:38.360 --> 42:39.627
<i>You're in Descartes chair.</i>

42:40.896 --> 42:42.329
<i>Easy there, buddy.</i>

42:42.463 --> 42:46.199
<i>I'm just gonna move
over to the couch.</i>

42:46.334 --> 42:48.334
<i>And then Descartes'
silly chair...</i>

42:48.468 --> 42:51.003
<i>will be all fine.</i>

42:54.707 --> 42:55.773
<i>Uh, Titus?</i>

42:55.908 --> 42:59.510
<i>The dog's
in Descartes' chair now.</i>

42:59.645 --> 43:01.945
<i>And he's rocking. Should
I tell him to get down?</i>

43:02.080 --> 43:05.048
<i>No, you shouldn't.
The dog is Descartes.</i>

43:05.183 --> 43:08.050
<i>Oh.</i>

43:08.185 --> 43:09.652
<i>Well.</i>

43:09.786 --> 43:11.120
<i>This is amazing.</i>

43:11.254 --> 43:13.489
<i>How did you teach him to
rock a chair like that?</i>

43:13.623 --> 43:16.091
<i>Don't make a stew
about it, Gus.</i>

43:16.225 --> 43:18.560
<i>You'll only
confuse him.</i>

43:18.694 --> 43:21.628
<i>Descartes' immediate
goal is humanity...</i>

43:21.763 --> 43:23.831
<i>as surely as ours
is divinity.</i>

43:23.965 --> 43:26.933
<i>What?</i>

43:27.067 --> 43:28.301
<i>Sorry. I guess...</i>

