44:45.534 --> 44:49.136
<i>All right. Why can't a
duffer like me catch a fish?</i>

44:50.372 --> 44:52.105
<i>Isn't the answer obvious?</i>

44:52.239 --> 44:54.741
<i>Isn't it because at my
present level of skill...</i>

44:54.875 --> 44:57.410
<i>the fish would have to be
so damn dumb...</i>

44:57.545 --> 45:00.212
<i>and utterly unelusive
as to be not worth catching?</i>

45:00.346 --> 45:01.980
<i>And how much more elusive...</i>

45:02.115 --> 45:04.649
<i>should a thing as wondrous
