45:04.783 --> 45:08.252
<i>Fishermen should be the
easiest of men to convince...</i>

45:08.387 --> 45:11.822
<i>to search for their souls,
because fishing is nothing but...</i>

45:11.956 --> 45:13.523
<i>the pursuit
of the elusive.</i>

45:13.658 --> 45:17.493
<i>How can you be so patient
in searching for fish...</i>

45:17.627 --> 45:20.096
<i>and so hasty
