<i>Could be.</i>

49:49.825 --> 49:51.325
<i>Okay. So how
do you suppose...</i>

49:51.459 --> 49:52.759
<i>I ought to fish
for mine?</i>

49:52.894 --> 49:55.395
<i>With a soul pole,
