49:55.530 --> 49:57.396
<i>Where do
I get one?</i>

49:57.531 --> 49:59.231
<i>Right here's good.</i>

49:59.366 --> 50:00.633
<i>This where you
got yours?</i>

50:00.767 --> 50:01.734
<i>I got mine here.</i>

50:01.868 --> 50:05.337
<i>You got yours
in there.</i>

50:11.476 --> 50:14.645
<i>I still can't figure out
where this soul pole is.</i>

50:14.779 --> 50:15.813
<i>Shall I show you?</i>

50:15.947 --> 50:16.679
<i>Can you?</i>

50:16.814 --> 50:18.181
<i>I can by analogy.</i>

50:18.315 --> 50:20.683
<i>But you'll have to answer
a few questions first.</i>

50:20.818 --> 50:22.185
<i>Fire away.</i>

50:22.319 --> 50:23.952
<i>All right.</i>

50:24.087 --> 50:27.889
<i>Where is Rodney,
