50:53.545 --> 50:54.412
<i>I will.</i>

50:54.546 --> 50:55.579
<i>Excellent.</i>

50:55.713 --> 50:58.448
<i>Can you get me
a couple of cues?</i>

50:58.583 --> 50:59.716
<i>Yeah. Two of them.</i>

50:59.851 --> 51:02.752
<i>Now, who
