51:08.457 --> 51:09.457
<i>I wish I knew.</i>

51:09.592 --> 51:10.592
<i>Excellent!</i>

51:10.726 --> 51:12.160
<i>And who controls
your destiny?</i>

51:12.294 --> 51:13.695
<i>Wish I knew that, too.</i>

51:13.829 --> 51:16.630
<i>Very good. And who will,
one day...</i>

51:16.765 --> 51:19.066
<i>consign your body
to a wormy grave?</i>

51:19.200 --> 51:20.334
<i>I wish I knew that, too.</i>

51:20.468 --> 51:21.334
<i>Perfect!</i>

51:21.468 --> 51:22.635
<i>Why is that perfect?</i>

51:22.770 --> 51:25.338
<i>All I'm saying is,
"Oh, I wish I knew. "</i>

51:25.472 --> 51:27.739
<i>Come on. Don't you
