51:40.918 --> 51:43.953
<i>That's to abandon the search
before it's even begun.</i>

51:44.088 --> 51:46.756
<i>Believe me, no one's ever
discovered any truth...</i>

51:46.891 --> 51:51.393
<i>by barfing up Sunday school
answers to questions.</i>

51:51.528 --> 51:54.028
<i>Now, you and I agreed,
did we not...</i>

51:54.163 --> 51:56.464
<i>that Rodney is oblivious...</i>

51:56.598 --> 51:59.033
<i>to everything save
some weight and varnish.</i>

51:59.168 --> 52:00.267
<i>We did.</i>

52:00.401 --> 52:02.736
<i>Therefore, does it follow...</i>

52:02.870 --> 52:05.338
<i>that he is
just as oblivious...</i>

52:05.473 --> 52:07.139
<i>to Gus?</i>

52:07.274 --> 52:09.275
<i>Even though Gus
is his maker?</i>

52:09.409 --> 52:12.545
<i>Even though Gus
controls his destiny?</i>

52:12.679 --> 52:14.078
<i>Even though Gus is-</i>

52:14.213 --> 52:17.682
<i>Let's go ahead and call it.
Gus is his essence.</i>

52:17.817 --> 52:18.817
<i>Yes, it follows.</i>

52:18.951 --> 52:21.518
<i>Then therefore,
is it possible...</i>

52:21.653 --> 52:23.487
<i>that maybe you and I...</i>

52:23.621 --> 52:24.788
<i>are just as oblivious...</i>

52:24.923 --> 52:26.389
<i>to the presence
of a Creator?</i>

52:26.523 --> 52:29.826
<i>Just as oblivious to a
controller of destiny?</i>

52:29.960 --> 52:32.727
<i>Just as oblivious
to our essence?</i>

52:32.862 --> 52:36.064
<i>An essence that wields you
and I even more deftly...</i>

52:36.199 --> 52:37.332
<i>than you wield Rodney.</i>

52:37.467 --> 52:40.868
<i>Sure, it's possible.</i>

52:41.002 --> 52:42.136
<i>Well, there you have it.</i>

52:42.270 --> 52:44.171
<i>Rodney is to Gus...</i>

52:44.306 --> 52:46.606
<i>as Gus is
to his essence.</i>

52:46.740 --> 52:49.075
<i>You name the essence soul
and you, sir...</i>

52:49.210 --> 52:50.743
<i>have your soul pole.</i>

52:50.878 --> 52:53.445
<i>Me?</i>

52:53.580 --> 52:56.381
<i>So, no matter how
hopelessly stupid I am...</i>

52:56.516 --> 53:01.419
<i>in comparison to my essence
or my soul...</i>

53:01.553 --> 53:05.589
<i>I still have
a profound purpose.</i>

53:05.723 --> 53:07.991
<i>I like that, Titus.</i>

53:08.125 --> 53:09.559
<i>I like that.</i>

53:09.694 --> 53:10.927
<i>Thank you.</i>

53:11.062 --> 53:14.730
<i>I swiped it
from Plotinus.</i>

